{"id":553093,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/03/小椰子君｜小镇故事：小镇的女人（二）/","date":"2017-03-02T03:59:42Z","modified":"2017-03-02T04:02:39Z","title":"小椰子君｜小镇故事：小镇的女人（二）","content":"<blockquote style=\"width: 65%;\"><p><strong>相关专题</strong>：<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/%E5%B7%AB%E5%B1%B1%E7%AB%A5%E5%85%BB%E5%AA%B3%E6%A1%88/\" target=\"_blank\">巫山童养媳案</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/u/2810875132\" target=\"_blank\">@小椰子君</a>：看到#巫山童养媳#想起我身边的她。在农村童养媳是很普遍的，别说在你的城市没有见过，你们身边没有发生的，不代表别的地方就没有，我从小到大所见到的童养媳们，真的没几个过的好的，大部分都是从早干活到晚，文化程度低下，很早就被嫁出去，彩礼给兄弟们用来娶媳妇，或者直接把童养媳许配给哥哥或者弟弟。所以请关注这个群体。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/a78a8cfcly1fd7rw9bslkj20rs9za1kx.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-553095\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/a78a8cfcly1fd7rw9bslkj20rs9za1kx.jpeg\" width=\"550\" height=\"7114\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/a78a8cfcly1fd7rw9bslkj20rs9za1kx.jpeg 1000w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/a78a8cfcly1fd7rw9bslkj20rs9za1kx-768x9933.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/a78a8cfcly1fd7rw9xnwaj20rs9clkjl.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-553094\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/a78a8cfcly1fd7rw9xnwaj20rs9clkjl.jpeg\" width=\"550\" height=\"6664\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/a78a8cfcly1fd7rw9xnwaj20rs9clkjl.jpeg 1000w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/a78a8cfcly1fd7rw9xnwaj20rs9clkjl-768x9306.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,9203],"tags":[13419,32411,27113,10686,32500,18979,9897,28226]}